        {
          "id": "unit-2",
          "title": "Real Estate Capital Structures",
          "description": "Equity, debt, and mezzanine financing structures.",
          "lessons": [
            {
              "id": "lesson-2-1",
              "title": "Capital Structures Overview",
              "type": "video",
              "duration": "60 min",
              "sections": [
                {
                  "type": "markdown",
                  "content": "## The Capital Stack\n\nReal estate deals are typically financed with a mix of **Debt** (Senior Mortgages) and **Equity** (LP/GP). More complex structures may involve Mezzanine Debt or Preferred Equity."
                },
                {
                  "type": "quiz",
                  "content": "Capital Stack Quiz",
                  "quizData": [
                    {
                      "id": "cap-1",
                      "text": "In a typical capital stack, which position has the highest risk and highest expected return?",
                      "type": "multiple-choice",
                      "options": [
                        "Senior Debt",
                        "Mezzanine Debt",
                        "Common Equity"
                      ],
                      "correctAnswer": "Common Equity",
                      "explanation": "Equity is the 'first loss' position but captures all the upside, thus commanding the highest return."
                    },
                    {
                      "id": "cap-2",
                      "text": "Which component is paid first from the property's cash flow?",
                      "type": "multiple-choice",
                      "options": [
                        "Senior Debt",
                        "Equity"
                      ],
                      "correctAnswer": "Senior Debt",
                      "explanation": "Senior lenders have priority of payment (and foreclosure rights) over all other stakeholders."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "video",
                  "content": "https://commondatastorage.googleapis.com/gtv-videos-bucket/sample/BigBuckBunny.mp4"
                },
                {
                  "type": "markdown",
